                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-932-18530815 t18530815-932-punishment-92"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Henry John King, inspector of the City police, stated that the prisoner was connected with a gang of forgers, three of whom had been transported.</hi>)</p>
